00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:58,850
<font size="64">- What the... - You turn away?</font>

1182
00:27:58,850 --> 00:28:02,420
<font size="64">- I believed you were doing well - He's finally here.</font>

1183
00:28:02,420 --> 00:28:03,990
