1186
00:28:05,320 --> 00:28:06,420
<font size="64">- That's it? - Also...</font>

1187
00:28:06,420 --> 00:28:09,090
<font size="64">Turn off the song. Turn it off.</font>

1188
00:28:06,490 --> 00:28:10,190
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He's been waiting all this time for these 4 seconds.)</font>

1189
00:28:09,330 --> 00:28:11,430
