1228
00:29:17,660 --> 00:29:19,530
<font size="64">- Five if you're a slave. - That's not fair.</font>

1229
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:21,230
<font size="64">- But... - That's harsh.</font>

1230
00:29:21,230 --> 00:29:23,700
<font size="64">- There's no reason to try. - Think about it.</font>

1231
00:29:22,670 --> 00:29:26,270
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They have to win to get coins.)</font>

1232
00:29:23,700 --> 00:29:24,730
<font size="64">You're a great director.</font>

