1260
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:03,010
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Only the Mafia gets a different song.)</font>

1261
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:01,600
<font size="64">Close your eyes and stomp if you're ready.</font>

1262
