<font size="64">- You must hide your identity... - And guess.</font>

1263
00:30:04,870 --> 00:30:07,980
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Round 1, the Mafia has been chosen.)</font>

1264
00:30:07,040 --> 00:30:08,040
