00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:11,040
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He sensed something already.)</font>

1291
00:31:11,410 --> 00:31:13,410
<font size="64">- I can tell. - Right away.</font>

1292
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:13,910
