1293
00:31:15,140 --> 00:31:19,350
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The Civilians are dancing techno.)</font>

1294
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:24,090
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He's alone in paradise.)</font>

1295
00:31:22,820 --> 00:31:23,950
<font size="64">Right away.</font>

1296
00:31:25,260 --> 00:31:27,120
<font size="64">Seok Sam is clueless.</font>

1297
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,690
<font size="64">Don't do that.</font>

1298
00:31:28,190 --> 00:31:29,490
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Right then)</font>

