00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:37,870
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(My gosh)</font>

1305
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:39,970
<font size="64">- Right away. - You can't do that.</font>

1306
00:31:37,870 --> 00:31:40,040
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He was in paradise.)</font>

1307
00:31:39,970 --> 00:31:42,610
<font size="64">- It's obvious. - It can't be obvious?</font>

1308
00:31:40,040 --> 00:31:42,470
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He saw the fan and switched.)</font>

1309
00:31:42,710 --> 00:31:46,710
