1310
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:46,580
<font size="64">He doesn't know the rules.</font>

1311
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:47,810
<font size="64">The only thing he knows is "Aftermath."</font>

1312
00:31:46,780 --> 00:31:49,650
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They wrap up quickly because of Kwang Hee's unexpected move.)</font>

1313
00:31:47,910 --> 00:31:49,210
<font size="64">He doesn't know the rule.</font>

1314
00:31:49,210 --> 00:31:51,110
<font size="64">- If you do it like that, - You shouldn't make it so obvious.</font>

1315
00:31:49,650 --> 00:31:51,350
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Nagging mode on)</font>

1316
00:31:51,110 --> 00:31:52,220
<font size="64">the Mafia would know...</font>

1317
00:31:52,220 --> 00:31:53,680
<font size="64">- what song it is. - You shouldn't overdo it.</font>

1318
00:31:53,680 --> 00:31:54,920
<font size="64">- Keep it moderate. - So I can't steal from others?</font>

