1320
00:31:54,920 --> 00:31:56,820
<font size="64">Do it only as much as your part in "Aftermath."</font>

1321
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,590
<font size="64">- Just enough to feel the vibe. - A little bit.</font>

1322
00:31:58,490 --> 00:32:01,920
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The 4-second singer was thrilled to get a solo shot after ages.)</font>

1323
00:31:58,590 --> 00:31:59,920
