1324
00:31:59,920 --> 00:32:01,660
<font size="64">- Just that much? - Yes.</font>

1325
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:03,730
<font size="64">- But it was so obvious. - Why?</font>

1326
00:32:03,730 --> 00:32:05,030
<font size="64">- I'm sorry. - You were the Mafia.</font>

1327
00:32:05,030 --> 00:32:07,330
<font size="64">No, wasn't it "Wa" by Lee Jung Hyun?</font>

1328
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:09,130
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(The Mafia is caught.)</font>

1329
00:32:07,330 --> 00:32:09,170
<font size="64">I never thought you'd Wasn't it that song?</font>

1330
00:32:09,170 --> 00:32:10,700
<font size="64">Everyone gets one point,</font>

1331
00:32:09,770 --> 00:32:12,900
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Each Civilian gets 1 point.)</font>

1332
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:12,140
<font size="64">except Jee Seok Jin, the Mafia.</font>

1333
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:14,640
<font size="64">You're only focused on securing your screen time.</font>

1334
00:32:12,900 --> 00:32:15,870
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(They almost failed because of the "After Effect" dancer.)</font>

1335
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,840
