1337
00:32:16,510 --> 00:32:19,780
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Round 2 of Dance Mafia begins.)</font>

1338
00:32:18,070 --> 00:32:19,840
<font size="64">- Eyes closed, stomp your feet. - Okay.</font>

1339
