1358
00:32:57,180 --> 00:32:59,620
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Suspicious)</font>

1359
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:01,550
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Is Seok Sam the Mafia again?)</font>

1360
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:02,720
