00:33:11,260 --> 00:33:14,300
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(Se Hee is just standing still.)</font>

1365
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,300
<font size="64">Look at her.</font>

1366
00:33:14,300 --> 00:33:16,300
<font size="64" color="#ffffcc">(He's sure of it.)</font>

1367
00:33:15,870 --> 00:33:17,670
